    <span class="anchor" id="tools-clearfix"></span>

    <h2>Clearfix</h2>

    <p>
        Clearfix is a rather legacy layout adjustment multi-selector. With Flexbox on the rise this tool will become outdated.
        Regardless, clearfix helps containing selectors keep their floating children within bounds.
        Without clearfix some floating selectors may escape the container.
    </p>

    <pre><code class="language-markup"><!--
        selector {
            @include clearfix();
        }
    --></code></pre>

